Privacy Policy for Body Measurement Size Tracker

Last updated: 12.11.2024

Welcome to the Body Measurement Size Tracker app! We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting it. This Privacy Policy outlines our practices regarding data collection, usage, and security to give you a clear understanding of our approach.

1. Personal Information
No Collection of Personal Information:
The Body Measurement Size Tracker app does not collect, obtain, or store any personal information. This includes any data that can identify you, such as name, email, or physical location.

No Access to Personal Information:
Since we do not collect or store any personal information, no one (including us) has access to it. Your data remains completely private to you and is not accessible by third parties or by us.

2. Data Security and Privacy
While the Body Measurement Size Tracker app does not collect any personal information, we are committed to ensuring that your usage remains private and secure.

On-Device Data Storage: All data you input, such as body measurements, is stored locally on your device. None of your information is sent to external servers, ensuring it remains accessible only to you.
No Internet Connectivity Required: Since we don’t collect data, our app doesn’t require an internet connection to function. This further ensures that your data remains private and does not leave your device.
No Third-Party Analytics or Advertising: We do not use any third-party analytics or advertising services that would otherwise require data access. This ensures there are no background processes or data sharing with external entities.
3. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices or legal obligations. If we make any material changes, we will notify you by updating the "Last Updated" date at the top of this policy. We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your privacy.

4. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please feel free to contact us at: app.supp05@gmail.com

Thank you for using Body Measurement Size Tracker, and rest assured that your privacy and data security are our top priorities.
